creator: Ackert, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Practice Pipeline is a simple business development system that keeps you focused on the relationships that matter most to your pipeline.

It has five key features that help you grow your pipeline.

1. TARGETS. Each one represents a key relationship and reminds you to connect with them regularly. Because business development is about people, not just tasks.

2. SHARING. Collaborate with your colleagues to close more business. Cross-sell more easily, expand client relationships, and gain better visibility into your business opportunities.

3. INSIGHTS. Our system uses metrics developed from thousands of hours of business development coaching to help you make the most of your Targets.

4. ALL YOUR DEVICES. We have apps for iOS, Android, macOS, and Windows. Stay on top of your pipeline no matter how you like to work.

5. INTEGRATION. (optional, but recommended) Practice Pipeline can integrate into most CRM platforms, eliminating the need for double-entry. Contact your administrator about syncing your Pipeline data with your CRM database.

This app works in conjunction with your corporate Practice Pipeline account. Log in with your existing Practice Pipeline credentials.

If you don't have a corporate Practice Pipeline account, ask your administrator about implementing Practice Pipeline at your firm.
descriptionShort: The simple and effective tool for business development and pipeline growth.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
***NEW FEATURES, NEW BRAND***

Our user base and features have grown so much that we have rebranded to celebrate. This app is now called PipelinePLUS, powered by Ackert, Inc. All our features are built on top of pipeline management, and now include all of our new-business offerings in one place: pipeline, e-learning, AI-driven insights, and analytics/reporting for managers. We have also built new features into the app, such as two-factor authentication and new categories for Insights.
